---
title: Shrimp with Lobster Ravioli in a Creamy Tomato Sauce with Zucchini Ribbons
description: This isn’t your usual ravioli: this is ravioli taken to the heights of luxury. The tender pasta shells are stuffed with lobster meat, so you know they’re going to be special. But it only gets better when you add in tender pink shrimp, turning this dish into a seafood celebration. With a creamy tomato sauce and ribbons of zucchini to finish it off, it becomes the sort of meal you’ll be proud to present as your own.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shrimp-with-lobster-ravioli-6f925197.jpg
